{"tid":1297021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民狙擊狗隻行動","createTime":"2019-07-08T14:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:13:30.000Z","uid":57801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9657a9992c865fd966c2e5d953bd8428c333899c","tid":1297021,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"全部人喺街到見到黑警都要狙擊佢地，佢地可以埋沒良知，但係唔會抵受到壓力。（從佢地讀唔成書同EQ 咁底可以見到）所以必需要令佢地頂唔順， 一見到有狗就大大聲屌佢地笑佢地，佢地只可以忍。佢地行一轉咇都要比人屌十幾次，令佢地成為過街老鼠， 唔敢着住制服見人。<br />\n之後再加埋放工都唔可以比佢地攰，識人/認得做狗嘅都見一次屌一次。服務業唔serve 佢地，營造做警犬=二等賤民嘅氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n最終要佢地明白<br />\n香港警察，胡亂執法<br />\n香港警察，知法犯法<br />\n香港警察，全部垃圾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察，吞_ _ _ </span>"},{"pid":"f701954ad56087bad6bcf3b8b424af65e1f0ce4b","tid":1297021,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"為所有比黑警打/拉/嚇嘅義士報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abc283f30788b47eb0151aafef737ec89fabc1c","tid":1297021,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"仲要為醫護，律師，老師同記者報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3cf3045302ce6afed663a99b8063daa79124e7","tid":1297021,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"見到畜牲 一定要搵人一齊屌"},{"pid":"4451c176573ac80c4a7b4630fdbc1f158b7a9d2c","tid":1297021,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFpXKks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFpXKks.png&h=bcf32b7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94792dc106368c1a716c656810e3458a1daac5fd","tid":1297021,"uid":57801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYzMCFN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYzMCFN.png&h=4e462af8&s={SIZ